{"title":"人民歌颂斯大林　（节录长诗“献给斯大林”）","authors":["艾青"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":12,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民歌颂斯大林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（节录长诗“献给斯大林”）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿我的这颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能长上翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象信鸽带着信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我带着希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过蒙古草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过大戈壁沙漠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过贝加尔湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过西伯利亚平原………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀着激动的欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我侧斜了翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投向莫斯科——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界的心脏…………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克里姆林宫前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我合上了翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用狂欢的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向斯大林歌唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林的功德，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超过天上的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林的事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使人民蒙受荣光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林的思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哺育全世界人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林的恩情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比海洋更深更广………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民歌颂斯大林——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是歌颂耶和华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不企求怜悯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不想望天堂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民歌颂斯大林——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的是你忠于人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你无比光辉的行动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实现了列宁的理想。……”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}